The paper discusses the design of a database system for the LSST project, which involves handling large volumes of data and real-time processing. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the database (cs.DB), distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), information retrieval (cs.IR), and software engineering (cs.SE) sub-categories.
